    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用乒乓球和乒乓球拍向上移动并到达目标！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有四个阶段： 简单阶段、普通阶段、困难阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有 3 个阶段。挑战自我，超越自我！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏方法是用鼠标移动乒乓球拍，这需要简单的反应能力。虽然简单的操作可以让您尽情享受动态破坏积木的乐趣，但沿途会有各种噱头和障碍等着您，因此想要前进并不容易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，玩家需要利用自己的反应能力征服各个阶段，突破一个又一个阻碍自己的噱头，体验惊险刺激的感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/ffeaf9f18f83116c0b78934cbbcaf82f.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/ffeaf9f18f83116c0b78934cbbcaf82f.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你玩腻了乒乓球，不妨试试击打电视。</p>",
